      <short value="Namespace to which this identifier belongs in the local system context (and possibly in any other openEHR compliant environment)"/>
      <definition value="Namespace to which this identifier belongs in the local system context (and possibly in any other openEHR compliant environment) e.g. terminology , demographic . These names are not yet standardised. Legal values for namespace are: 'local', 'unknown', or a string matching the standard regex [a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_.:/&amp;?=+-]*. Note that the first two are just special values of the regex, and will be matched by it."/>
